Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笼中鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的口袋本好像也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:21:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是中央种子岛高中机器人研究部的各位吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有件事情想要告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我们走一趟吗
